                Laptop 💻 ---------> Hardware ⚙️



what is virtualization layer??

That layer actually Hypervisor.

Hypervisor=>It is software that creates and run virtual machine (VMs).




                     What the Hypervisor do?


                     Laptop 💻 (Host System)
                     - 8 GB RAM
                     - 100 GB HDD
                            |
                     [Hypervisor 🔄]
                              |
      -----------------------------------------------------
      |                                                   |
     VM1 (Linux 🐧)                                    VM2 (Windows 🪟)
     - 2 GB RAM                                          - 2 GB RAM
     - 10 GB HDD                                         - 10 GB HDD




                    

